{"tid":747248,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地人報稱買倫敦金受騙涉逾80億人幣到港請願","createTime":"2018-07-18T08:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T09:01:10.000Z","uid":26769,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9cfd75b309875f2daa19e9b17828af5a45ad29b5","tid":747248,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:37:14.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】約30名內地人懷疑受騙購買倫敦金，今早在禮賓府外向特首林鄭月娥遞交請願信。<br />\n<br />\n這一批人報稱來自內地23個省市，他們指，有6間香港公司開設合共12個跨境網上平台教授買賣倫敦金的課程，由騙徒扮演老師及成功搵快錢的人士誘導人購買倫敦金。他們報稱有三萬名內地人受騙，涉及金額達82.5億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n他們其後到灣仔警察總部門外向警務處處長盧偉聰遞交請願信。有苦主表示，曾三次到有關公司查詢，最後獲告知不作賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解唔係大陸請願呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0b2abde200136e306fa726a0875664e6f0179a","tid":747248,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:39:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99569b925b3654f8a5061bb737c52b6d6dfe1cfb","tid":747248,"uid":78399,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:40:34.000Z","msg":"唔係大陸人被人呃， 政府點會肯咁落力拉人"},{"pid":"fa1ba26b326242e560dc2cd08de7b5dba401786d","tid":747248,"uid":154106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/170100_db61039a4d29bcbdd0097ea700c74a01.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F170100_db61039a4d29bcbdd0097ea700c74a01.jpeg&h=b825752d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我剩係想講"}]}